data.description: This lovely modern Ranch has 3 bedrooms, 2 bath and fully finished basement! Located off route 9 for an easy commute, near shopping centers and near Freehold Raceway. This home has Hardwood floor throughout most of the home, Kitchen has Granite countertops with a beautiful farm-sink. Central Air and Heating. Also, features an Energy Efficient from Tesla, Solar panels that are transferable.  Call and Schedule a tour today !!
